https://rosting.by

#Functional Test Cases

Test case 1
Steps:
1. Go to https://rosting.by
2.In "tours window" Select  "Минск" in "откуда" 
3.Select "Египет" in "куда" 
4.Select "7" & "15" in "ночей"
5.Select "13.10.2021" & "12.11.2021" in "Период вылетов"
6.Click button "Найти"
Expected Result:
will display a list of tours

Test case 2
Steps:

1.in the window that appears, select the first round
2.Click button "Подробнее"
Expected Result:
 information about this course will be dropped
 
Test case 3.
Steps:
1.in the window that appears click button "Отправить заявку"
Expected Result:
  see the application form

Test case 4.
Steps:
1.In the dropped form 
fill in all fields where there is an asterisk
2.click on button "Отправить заявку"
 Expected Result: the form should be submitted and the site should notify about its submission

Test case 5.
Steps:
1.  Go to https://rosting.by
2. in the section "Самые выгодные предложения" click button "забронировать" at first tour
Expected Result:
see the form from test case 4

Test case 6.
Steps:
1.  Go to https://rosting.by
2. In the main section click on advertising 
3.go to page "подбор тура"
4.Select 12 in "взрослых"
5.Select 3 in "детей"
6.Select 3 in "возраст детей"
Expected Result:
shouldn't show tours

Test case 7
Steps:
1. Go to https://rosting.by
2. In the main section Select "Авиабилеты" between "Туры" & "Авиабилеты"
3.Select "Минск,Беларусь" in "город вылета"
4.Select "Москва(Домодево)" in "город прибытия"
5.Select "дату" in field "туда" & "обратно" 
6.select 1 in "пассажир"
Expected Result:
go to https://tickets.rosting.by/flights/.. and see possible tickets

Test case 8
Steps:
1. Go to https://rosting.by
2. in the navigation click "отели"
3. Click button "заказать звонок"
4.fill in the correct phone number input field
5.click button "БУДУ ЖДАТЬ"
Expected Result:
see a message about successful form submission

Test case 9
Steps:
1. Go to https://rosting.by
2. in the navigation click "отели"
3. Click button "заказать звонок"
4.fill in the empty phone number input field
5.click button "БУДУ ЖДАТЬ"
Expected Result:
see alert with an error in filling out the number

Test case 10
Steps:
1. Go to https://rosting.by
2. in the navigation click "страны"
3.select "Египет" in list 
4.click button "забронировать" in first hotel
5.in the window that appears click button "Отправить заявку"
Expected Result:
  see the application form
